{
  "stem": "27443.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Being that we arrived from Majdanek in very poor-- in a very poor situation, without having any assets to our own, just the clothes on our back, what was given to us, hungry.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It happened one day that I met at work a boy that approached me and asked me from where I am and where I was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I told him from where I am, he somehow became a very good friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He shared bread with me whenever I didn't have, because he had more than I had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because as I said, he came from home, and he had a lot of things, like bedding and clothes, because he came straight from home to this camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he had his two brothers and his father and a sister were hidden by the Poles, not in camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after a while, when we were in the camp, the Poles gave away to the German-- gave away his sister and his father, and they were brought into camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The father was a sick man, and he died into my-- my arms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The sister was a beautiful young woman, and she had a child living with Poles, hidden by Poles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she was brought in, into camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And poor thing, she was running around in camp, screaming, where is my child?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And where is my child?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as we were marching out from camp to work, she was shot by the gate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "David and I, we became very good friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, he shared a lot of clothes and food with me, which made me easier survive the situation that I was in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had no food, as I said.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
